ygData.messageBody:
As harsh as it sounds, I care not for Greater
Fay, though it is the birthplace of my mother, and the
home of the Mother's children. I am concerned with the
Bloodsabres and their attempt to summon forth the power of
the Plaguebearer. You can expect me to be at either
the gates of Qeynos or the entrance to my fair Glade
to turn back the forces of the Plague.<br>Evil has
tread upon the grounds of Qeynos for too long, and I
will work my best to remove the stain.<br>May Tunare
be with us all.<br><br>Nukai Oakenwulf<br>Chief
Druid Executive of Spiritus Valorum
